WEBVTT

00:00:59.343 --> 00:01:02.576
Hruaitu lawng siloin zultu hna 
hmaisuam ve zong abiapi,

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:06.496
zeicatiah, zultuthar nih zultu hmasa 
hna an izohchunh hna.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:09.572
Hi, an tam deuh thluahmah cang,
tlawmpal ah,

00:01:09.596 --> 00:01:10.976
mi pathum an ichap cang.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:13.420
Thazang a cak tuk cang,
tlauh khawh asi tilo.

00:01:13.444 --> 00:01:15.221
Tucu, cawlcanghnak a thawk cang.

00:01:15.245 --> 00:01:16.245
(Nihthawng)

00:01:16.651 --> 00:01:18.976
Si, zohhmanh, mi an tam deuh ahcun,

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.564
hna a ngam deuh suaumau.

00:01:20.588 --> 00:01:22.819
Tuandeuh ah a thu sasawhmi hna kha,

00:01:22.843 --> 00:01:24.353
itel ve an duh cang.

00:01:24.377 --> 00:01:27.717
An thiamtuk rih men lai lo,
nihsawh an si lai lo.

00:01:27.741 --> 00:01:30.550
nain khulhrang in an ti ahcun,
zapi lakah an itel ve ko lai.